Cliffjumper reaches the top, and jumps up slightly, landing on the dust,
as he slowly slides down, his arms up to give him ballance. When he
landed at the bottom he began to look around. He walked up towards
Caliburst's unconciouss form. "Well, we probably should take out this
Con first." Cliffjumper held out his gun, and clicked back the loading
area, then he smile. "Bye bye Decepticrap." he said, and began to pull
the trigger.
